Step 1
Open the VLC media player.

Step 2
Click the "Media" button on the top navigation bar to show the File menu.

Step 3
Click the "Open Network Stream" option or Press Ctrl + N .

Step 4
Paste following URL into the "URL" input box.

https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Shadmanislam/bdiptv/master/BD%20IPTV.m3u

Step 5
Open playlist to select channels.
